#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:302
msgid ""
"Layer containing (parts of) features from the input layer not overlapping "
"features from the overlay layers."
msgstr ""
"Sloj koji sadrži (delove) objekata iz ulaznog sloja koji se ne preklapaju sa"
" objektima iz slojeva preklapanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:308
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:multidifference``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:multidifference``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:318
msgid "Extract/clip by extent"
msgstr "Izdvoj/iseci po obuhvatu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:319
msgid ""
"Creates a new vector layer that only contains features which fall within a "
"specified extent. Any features which intersect the extent will be included "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"Pravi novi vektorski sloj koji sadrži samo objekte koji padaju unutar "
"zadatog obuhvata. Svi objekti koji se seku sa obuhvatom biće podrazumevano "
"uključeni."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:326
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:334
msgid ""
"Extract operation between a three-feature input layer 'a' and a dashed "
"extent (left) - resulting features with dashed extent for reference (right)"
msgstr ""
"Operacija izdvajanja između ulaznog sloja „a“ sa tri objekta i isprekidanog "
"obuhvata (levo) — rezultujući objekti sa isprekidanim obuhvatom radi "
"poređenja (desno)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:329
msgid "Optionally, feature geometries can also be clipped to the extent."
msgstr "Opciono, geometrije objekata mogu se i isecati na obuhvat."

