msgstr "Obuhvat za isecanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:3
msgid "Available methods are:"
msgstr "Dostupni metodi su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:5
msgid ""
"Calculate from layer…: uses extent of a layer loaded in the current project"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz sloja…: koristi obuhvat sloja učitanog u tekućem projektu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:6
msgid ""
"Calculate from layout map…: uses extent of a :ref:`layout map item "
"<layout_map_item>` in the active project"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz karte rasporeda…: koristi obuhvat :ref:`stavke karte u "
"rasporedu <layout_map_item>` u aktivnom projektu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:8
msgid ""
"Calculate from bookmark…: uses extent of a saved :ref:`bookmark "
"<sec_bookmarks>`"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iz obeleživača…: koristi obuhvat sačuvanog :ref:`obeleživača "
"<sec_bookmarks>`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:9
msgid "Use map canvas extent"
msgstr "Koristi obuhvat platna karte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:10
msgid ""
"Draw on canvas: click and drag a rectangle delimiting the area to take into "
"account"
msgstr ""
"Nacrtaj na platnu: klikom i prevlačenjem nacrtajte pravougaonik koji "
"ograničava područje koje se uzima u obzir"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:11
msgid "Enter the coordinates as ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"
msgstr "Unesite koordinate kao ``xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:364
msgid "**Clip features to extent**"
msgstr "**Iseci objekte na obuhvat**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:365
msgid "``CLIP``"
msgstr "``CLIP``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:366
msgid "[boolean]"
msgstr "[logička vrednost]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:368
msgid "Default: False"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: False"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:369
msgid ""
"If checked, the geometries will be clipped to the extent chosen instead of "
"taking the whole geometry as output. Moreover, output geometries will be "
"automatically converted to multi geometries to ensure uniform output types."
msgstr ""
"Ako je uključeno, geometrije će biti isečene na izabrani obuhvat umesto da "
"se cela geometrija uzme kao izlaz. Osim toga, izlazne geometrije biće "
"automatski pretvorene u višedelne geometrije radi obezbeđivanja "
"jednoobraznih izlaznih tipova."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:373
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:398
msgid "**Extracted**"
msgstr "**Izdvojeno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:378
msgid ""
"Specify the layer to contain the features from the input layer that are "
"inside the clip extent. :ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte sloj koji sadrži objekte iz ulaznog sloja koji su unutar obuhvata "
"isecanja. :ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:401
msgid "Layer containing the clipped features."
msgstr "Sloj koji sadrži isečene objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:406
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:extractbyextent``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:extractbyextent``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:416
msgid "Intersection"
msgstr "Presek"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:417
msgid ""
"Extracts the portions of features from the input layer that overlap features"
" in the overlay layer."
msgstr ""
"Izdvaja delove objekata iz ulaznog sloja koji se preklapaju sa objektima u "
"sloju preklapanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:420
msgid ""
"Features in the intersection layer are assigned the attributes of the "
"overlapping features from both the input and overlay layers."
msgstr ""
"Objektima u sloju preseka dodeljuju se atributi preklapajućih objekata iz "
"ulaznog sloja i sloja preklapanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:430
msgid ""
"Intersection operation between a two-feature input layer 'a' and a single "
"feature overlay layer 'b' (left) - overlapping areas become a new two-"
"feature layer with both layers' attributes (right)"
msgstr ""
"Operacija preseka između ulaznog sloja „a“ sa dva objekta i sloja "
"preklapanja „b“ sa jednim objektom (levo) — preklapajuće oblasti postaju "
"novi sloj sa dva objekta i atributima oba sloja (desno)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:437
msgid ""
"This algorithm drops existing primary keys or FID values and regenerates "
"them in output layers."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam uklanja postojeće primarne ključeve ili FID vrednosti i "
"ponovo ih generiše u izlaznim slojevima."

